enum _CPConstraint

Enumeration of constraint types used in spring and strut model.

Enumerator:
CPConstraintNone  No constraint. Free movement, equivalent to 'spring'.
CPConstraintFixed  Distance is fixed. Equivalent to a 'strut'.
